title: 2022 let’s do this

description:
Brooke and Danielle are in the studio this week recapping 2021 & sharing their goals for 2022!  The gals discuss their words of the year, resolutions, and favorites from last year. Brooke and Danielle also get into their winter breaks at home, and what they have been up to since being back in NYC!  Be sure to tag @galsonthegopodcast in your listening selfies/stories!
